t%3BGeneric%2C%20AI-generated%20applications%20can%20fail%20to%20stand%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20relying%20on%20AI%20without%20reviewing%20its%20output%20can%20lead%20to%20mistakes%20or%20misrepresentations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruitment%20and%20AI%20pros%20explained%20to%20BI%20the%20dos%20and%20don'ts%20of%20using%20these%20tools%20and%20how%20candidates%20can%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20technology%20available%20when%20job%20hunting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e661fb5e-9598-4d0f-add7-75e8a045a15a%5C%22%3EMock%20tests%2C%20interviews%2C%20and%20portfolios%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Uffindell%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20graduate%20recruitment%20platform%20Bright%20Network%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20AI%20can%20be%20very%20advantageous%20in%20the%20job%20hunt%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-help-recruit-hire-employees-tech-women-bias-job-seeking-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eespecially%20for%20underrepresented%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20neurodiverse%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20helps%20level%20the%20playing%20field%20by%20offering%20better%20preparation%20opportunities%2C%20such%20as%20practice%20assessments%20and%20mock%20interviews%2C%20that%20may%20not%20have%20been%20otherwise%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandidates%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20many%20tools%2C%20such%20as%20CV%20builders%20like%20Kickresume%20and%20mock%20interview%20platforms%20like%20Interview%20Warmup%20by%20Google.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findeed-pathfinder-ai-job-candidates-tool%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndeed's%20Pathfinder%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20helps%20people%20discover%20career%20paths%20that%20fit%20their%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Heilman%2C%20the%20senior%20VP%20of%20product%2C%20automation%2C%20and%20AI%20at%20the%20staffing%20industry%20software%20company%20Bullhorn%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20company%20has%20a%20screening%20agent%20where%20candidates%20can%20conduct%20their%20first%20interview%20with%20an%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20could%20one%20day%20replace%20resumes%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20really%20get%20to%20see%20so%20much%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Heilman%20said%20of%20the%20technology.%20%26quot%3BIt%20unlocks%20so%20much%20more%20of%20the%20person's%20potential%20beyond%20what%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20could%20ever%20capture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeilman%20said%20it%20benefits%20candidates%20to%20be%20responsive%20and%20open%20to%20changes%2C%20even%20if%20it%20feels%20a%20bit%20strange%20at%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20willing%20to%20try%20out%20these%20screeners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BLean%20into%20the%20opportunities%20to%20respond%2C%20and%20lean%20in%20when%20you%20are%20faced%20with%20new%20AI%20tools%20like%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECori%20Lunnen%2C%20the%20VP%20of%20recruitment%20marketing%20operations%20at%20HireClix%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20candidates%20should%20not%20hesitate%20to%20use%20AI%20tools%20to%20create%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20cover%20letter%2C%20or%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20future%20is%20undeniably%20AI-driven%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20some%20recruiters%20will%20want%20to%20see%20examples%20of%20how%20a%20candidate%20can%20successfully%20integrate%20AI-generated%20content%20with%20their%20own%20creativity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20should%20be%20to%20use%20AI%20as%20a%20starting%20place%2C%20Lunnen%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20then%20ultimately%20create%20something%20more%20unique%20or%20tailored%20to%20the%20opportunity%20it's%20designed%20to%20engage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290d57b28-0de2-411c-a384-eea4228df23b%5C%22%3EBe%20careful%20with%20prompts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Jennifer%20Burns%2C%20director%20of%20career%20development%20of%20Cornell%20University's%20executive%20MBA%20program%2C%20learning%20to%20put%20in%20the%20right%20prompts%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20advises%20candidates%20to%20put%20their%20resumes%20into%20ChatGPT%20along%20with%20the%20job%20description%20and%20ask%20a%20question%20like%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20the%2010%20most%20important%20skills%20and%20keywords%20a%20hiring%20manager%20will%20look%20for%20to%20fill%20this%20role%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20most%20useful%20output%2C%20you%20want%20to%20begin%20with%20input.%20For%20example%2C%20you%20can%20provide%20details%20such%20as%20your%20degree%2C%20your%20major%2C%20and%20your%20past%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Burns%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpodcasts%2Fyour-money-matters%2Fhow-to-use-ai-to-help-with-your-job-search%2Fc6454246-dd7c-4007-b7f8-4aa38bd8f86c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20also%20input%20information%20about%20your%20major%20accomplishments%2C%20some%20of%20your%20highlights%2C%20and%20what%20motivates%20you%2C%20thinking%20about%20what%20you're%20good%20at%20and%20what%20you%20like%20doing.%20Then%2C%20after%20you%20share%20that%20information%2C%20you%20can%20ask%20specific%20questions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurns%20said%20AI%20tools%20can%20also%20help%20you%20determine%20good%20questions%20to%20ask%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20warned%20that%20candidates%20must%20ensure%20that%20everything%20makes%20sense%20and%20that%20they%20have%20a%20thorough%20understanding%20of%20the%20role.%20%26quot%3BJust%20putting%20in%20keywords%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20putting%20them%20in%20to%20match%20a%20job%20description%20isn't%20going%20to%20serve%20you%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237c88c1e-e631-46c5-badd-b9ec6649b9fc%5C%22%3EA%20personal%20touch%20is%20still%20important%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20recruiter's%20side%2C%20implementing%20AI%20can%20free%20up%20mental%20bandwidth%2C%20previously%20dominated%20by%20administrative%20tasks%20like%20scheduling%2C%20so%20recruiters%20can%20focus%20on%20providing%20a%20better%20experience%20for%20the%20candidates%20who%20move%20to%20the%20next%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20has%20its%20downsides%20too.%20Uffindell%20said%20some%20recruiters%20are%20seeing%20a%20500%25%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20applications%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-employers-know-ai-used-job-application-resume-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportant%20to%20still%20stand%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20view%20AI%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20support%2C%20not%20replace%2C%20your%20own%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20Uffindell%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20AI%20can%20help%20streamline%20the%20process%2C%20relying%20on%20it%20too%20heavily%20can%20lead%20to%20generic%20applications%20that%20fail%20to%20showcase%20a%20candidate's%20unique%20qualities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVrijen%20Attawar%2C%20a%20former%20career%20coach%20and%20now%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20AI-powered%20career%20guidance%20platform%20Careerspan%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20in%20this%20current%20environment%2C%20candidates%20should%20apply%20to%20fewer%20jobs%20so%20as%20to%20%26quot%3Bnot%20contribute%20to%20the%20application%20spam%20pile.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAvoid%20the%20temptation%20to%20use%20easy%20apply%20or%20other%20similar%20tools%20to%20apply%20for%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20save%20your%20time%20and%20sanity%20for%20the%20opportunities%20you%20can%20verify%20are%20real%20and%20excite%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20AI%20tools%20have%20limitations.%20Some%20make%20things%20up%20or%20exaggerate%20information%2C%20so%20it%20is%20a%20candidate's%20responsibility%20to%20proofread%20everything%20and%20ensure%20it%20is%20accurate%20before%20submitting%20an%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChatGPT%204's%20knowledge%20cut-off%20is%20April%202023%2C%20for%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20Uffindell%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20any%20major%20industry%20updates%20or%20company%20changes%20since%20then%20won't%20be%20included%20in%20ChatGPT%20outputs%2C%20so%20you'll%20need%20to%20do%20your%20own%20research%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUffindell%20said%20personalizing%20each%20application%20to%20the%20specific%20role%20is%20still%20crucial%20because%20employers%20are%20looking%20for%20candidates%20who%20can%20communicate%20their%20strengths%20well%20and%20who%20have%20good%20soft%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20strongest%20applications%20will%20combine%20AI's%20efficiency%20with%20the%20candidate's%20own%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BShowcasing%20not%20only%20the%20right%20skills%20but%20also%20the%20ability%20to%20navigate%20AI's%20limitations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-the-most-ai-looking-for-job-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735721041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673f3bf0ede4eeae3928c34c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-the-most-ai-looking-for-job-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20is%20transforming%20job%20searches%2C%20for%20both%20candidates%20and%20recruiters.%20Pros%20share%20their%20dos%20and%20don'ts%20for%20making%20the%20most%20of%20the%20tools%20available.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40businessinsider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-the-most-ai-looking-for-job-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EPFO%2C%20UPI%2C%20GST%20And%20Visa%3A%20These%20Things%20Will%20Change%20Starting%20January%201%2C%202025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStarting%20January%201%2C%202025%2C%20a%20slew%20of%20regulatory%20and%20financial%20changes%20will%20be%20coming%20into%20effect%2C%20affecting%20citizens%20across%20the%20country.%20From%20changes%20in%20the%20Employees'%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20(EPFO)%20procedures%20to%20adjustments%20in%20LPG%20pricing%20and%20the%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20(UPI)%2C%20the%20new%20year%20could%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20your%20wallet.%20Here's%20a%20complete%20list%20of%20the%20changes%20that%20you%20can%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEPFO%20new%20rule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEPFO%20is%20set%20to%20streamline%20the%20pension%20withdrawal%20process%20from%20January%201%2C%202025%20as%20part%20of%20the%20centralised%20pension%20payment%20system%20(CPPS).%20Pensioners%20will%20now%20have%20the%20convenience%20of%20withdrawing%20their%20pensions%20from%20any%20bank%20in%20the%20country%2C%20eliminating%20the%20hassle%20of%20additional%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20suggest%20that%20EPFO%20will%20be%20soon%20issuing%20an%20ATM%20card%20that%20will%20enable%20subscribers%20to%20withdraw%20money%20around%20the%20clock.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20EPF%20contribution%20cap%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20eliminated%20this%20year%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGST%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMulti-factor%20authentication%20(MFA)%20will%20be%20made%20mandatory%20for%20taxpayers%20for%20better%20security%20on%20the%20GST%20portal.%20Additionally%2C%20E-Way%20Bills%20(EWBs)%20can%20only%20be%20generated%20for%20base%20documents%20not%20older%20than%20180%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUPI%20and%20farmer%20loans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20recent%20circular%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%2C%20starting%20today%2C%20UPI%20123Pay%2C%20using%20which%20feature%20phone%20users%20make%20online%20payments%2C%20will%20see%20an%20increase%20in%20its%20transaction%20limit%20from%20January%201%2C%202025.%20The%20new%20limit%20will%20be%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20up%20from%20the%20previous%20Rs%205%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20has%20raised%20the%20cap%20on%20unsecured%20loans%20for%20farmers%20to%20Rs%202%20lakh%20from%20Rs%201.60%20lakh.%20This%20increase%2C%20effective%20today%2C%20is%20intended%20to%20provide%20more%20financial%20support%20to%20farmers%2C%20potentially%20aiding%20in%20better%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EVisa%20requirements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20Visa%20Appointment%20Reschedule%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20January%201%2C%202025%2C%20non-immigrant%20visa%20applicants%20in%20India%20will%20benefit%20from%20a%20policy%20allowing%20one%20free%20rescheduling%20of%20their%20visa%20appointment.%20However%2C%20any%20further%20rescheduling%20will%20necessitate%20a%20new%20application%20and%20payment%20of%20the%20visa%20fee%2C%20aiming%20to%20streamline%20the%20process%20while%20maintaining%20discipline%20in%20appointment%20scheduling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanges%20in%20the%20H-1B%20Visa%20Process%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20rules%2C%20effective%20from%20January%2017%2C%202025%2C%20will%20modernise%20the%20H-1B%20visa%20process%2C%20making%20it%20more%20flexible%20for%20employers%20and%20accessible%20for%20Indian%20F-1%20visa%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELPG%20pricing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government%20on%20Wednesday%20(Jan%201)%20slashed%20prices%20of%20commercial%20cylinders%20(19%20kg)%20from%20Rs%201818.50%20to%20Rs%201804%2C%20across%20cities%2C%20including%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai.%C2%A0However%2C%20the%20price%20of%20domestic%20LPG%20cylinders%20(14.2%20kg)%20remains%20unchanged%20at%20Rs%20803.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publi