n%20Ukraine%20said%20being%20able%20to%20see%20Russian%20drone%20feeds%20is%20%26quot%3Buseful%20because%20you%20see%20where%20the%20enemy%20drone%20that%20wants%20to%20destroy%20you%20is%20flying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20gives%20the%20unit%20a%20chance%20to%20take%20defensive%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20soldiers%20look%20at%20a%20large%20screen%20with%20an%20aerial%20view%20of%20Bakhmut%20and%20a%20plume%20of%20smoke%20on%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65843e7ecefc010bea261838%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20watch%20a%20drone%20feed%20from%20an%20underground%20command%20center%20in%20Bakhmut.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FLibkos%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESamuel%20Bendett%2C%20a%20drone%20expert%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Naval%20Analyses%2C%20described%20it%20as%20the%20wartime%20version%20of%20a%20common%20civilian%20occurrence.%20When%20you%20drive%20in%20your%20car%20and%20have%20your%20radio%20at%20a%20certain%20frequency%2C%20your%20radio%20can%20flip%20between%20different%20stations%20that%20use%20the%20same%20frequency.%20That%20is%20what%20is%20happening%20right%20now%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Bendett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236224ff5-2790-4ae1-a9c9-6303c2aa391f%5C%22%3EFight%20for%20the%20spectrum%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJackie%2C%20a%20US%20veteran%20fighting%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20there%20are%20two%20fights%20when%20we're%20fighting%20with%20drones.%20There's%20one%20that%20you%20can%20see%20on%20video.%20And%20there's%20one%20that's%20completely%20invisible.%26quot%3B%20That%20invisible%20fight%20is%20the%20fight%20in%20the%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%20or%20%26quot%3Bfight%20for%20the%20spectrum.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%20can%20get%20%26quot%3Bfull%26quot%3B%20and%20get%20%26quot%3Bcrow