20spectrum%20through%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20both%20sides%20are%20experiencing%20all%20the%20advantages%20and%20disadvantages%20of%20these%20developments.%20Sometimes%20Ukraine%20is%20collecting%20intel%2C%20and%20sometimes%20it's%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feed%20can%20help%20operators%20helplessly%20realize%20an%20attack%20is%20incoming%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bit%20also%20can%20be%20very%20informative%20for%20drone%20crews%2C%20experienced%20ones%20to%20kind%20of%20determine%20the%20tactic%20of%20the%20adversary%2C%20how%20far%20the%20drone%20flies%2C%20how%20fast%20it%20flies%2C%20what's%20the%20drone%20route%2C%20what%20the%20drone%20is%20looking%20for%2C%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth%2C%26quot%3B%20Bendett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20a%20hard%20thing%20to%20plan%20for%20given%20the%20chaotic%20nature%20of%20these%20occurrences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackie%20shared%20that%20Ukraine%20has%20attempted%20to%20%26quot%3Bplay%20games%20with%20the%20signals%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20Gregory%20Falso%2C%20an%20autonomous%20systems%20and%20cybersecurity%20expert%20at%20Cornell%20University%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bit's%20probably%20not%20predictable%20when%20you'd%20be%20able%20to%20get%20these%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%20It's%20more%20about%20seizing%20the%20advantage%20when%20the%20opportunity%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be2e906f-d532-428b-8a7c-852875b6ed10%5C%22%3ESwitching%20signals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFalco%20said%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20tell%20if%20the%20enemy%20has%20access%20to%20a%20feed%20because%20%26quot%3Byou%20don't%20have%20absolute%20certainty%20of%20where%20your%20band%20is%20at%20a%20given%20time%20and%20where%20you're%20projecting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ukraine%20drone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651d49e92ce014759e74522e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20serviceman%20launches%20a%20drone%20during%20a%20press%20tour%20in%20the%20Zhytomyr%20Region.%3Cp%3EKirill%20Chubotin%20%2F%20Ukrinform%2FFuture%20Publishing%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20questions%20about%20whether%20this%20could%20be%20taken%20further%2C%20though%2C%20going%20from%20accidental%20insight%20to%20deliberately%20pirated%20drones.%20Right%20now%2C%20that's%20more%20theory%20than%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20any%20Ukrainian%20or%20Russian%20operators%20could%20actually%20get%20control%20of%20the%20other%20side's%20drone%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20being%20able%20to%20see%20through%20its%20eyes%2C%20probably%20depends%20on%20the%20drone%2C%20Falco%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20the%20spectral%20bands%20used%20to%20see%20drone%20feeds%20are%20likely%20very%20different%20from%20the%20ones%20that%20control%20it.%20And%20the%20bands%20used%20to%20receive%20signals%20%E2%80%94%20that%20let%20the%20operator%20see%20what%20the%20drone%20can%20see%20%E2%80%94%20are%20typically%20less%20protected%20than%20the%20ones%20that%20send%20the%20signals%2C%20which%20is%20how%20operators%20tell%20drones%20what%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20feed%20switching%20is%20%26quot%3Bbound%20to%20happen%26quot%3B%20with%20so%20many%20drones%20in%20the%20sky%20and%20with%20different%20types%20of%20electronic%20warfare%20in%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolutions%2C%20Falco%20said%2C%20could%20involve%20something%20like%20added%20encryptions%20for%20drone%20feeds.%20But%20given%20the%20fast-moving%2C%20chaotic%2C%20and%20desperate%20nature%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20fighting%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20drone%20operators%20can%20go%20through%20multiple%20drones%20a%20day%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20worth%20it.%20And%20if%20that's%20the%20case%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20thing%20will%20keep%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20was%20the%20type%20of%20thing%20civilians%20would%20f