ong%20habits%20of%20lying%20and%20deceit%20and%20bring%20meaningful%20change%20within%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20neither%20vision%20nor%20candidates%20for%20the%20Delhi%20election.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20wants%20to%20win%20this%20election%20somehow%20by%20using%20dishonest%20means.%20But%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20won't%20let%20this%20happen.%20We%20won't%20let%20them%20win%20by%20using%20the%20tactics%20they%20are%20said%20to%20have%20used%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20asking%20Delhiites%20to%20keep%20checking%20names%20on%20voter%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20launched%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Lotus%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20constituency%20that%20he%20represents.%20%26quot%3BIn%2015%20days%2C%20they%20have%20put%20in%20applications%20to%20delete%20names%20of%205%2C000%20voters%20and%20also%20applied%20for%20the%20addition%20of%207%2C500%20names%20to%20the%20voter%20list.%20The%20total%20votes%20in%20my%20constituency%20is%201%20lakh%206%20thousand.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20holding%20an%20election%20then%3F%20A%20game%20is%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20name%20of%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20said%20a%20summary%20revision%20was%20carried%20out%20earlier%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20released%20a%20revised%20voter%20list%20on%20October%2029.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20a%2012%20per%20cent%20difference%20as%20the%20BJP%20claims%2C%20was%20the%20poll%20body's%20summary%20revision%20wrong%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20plans%20to%20get%20people%20from%20outside%20and%20register%20them%20as%20Delhi%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERefuting%20the%20charges%2C%20Delhi%20BJP%20chief%20Virendraa%20Sachdeva%20said%20the%20number%20of%20voters%20in%20Delhi%20saw%20a%20huge%