are%20that%20Manipur%20is%20in%20turmoil%20today%20because%20of%20the%20past%20sins%20committed%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20such%20as%20the%20repeated%20settlement%20of%20Burmese%20refugees%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20SoO%20Agreement%20with%20Myanmar-based%20militants%20in%20the%20state%2C%20spearheaded%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FA0X9urZ7M6%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FA0X9urZ7M6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20(%40NBirenSingh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNBirenSingh%2Fstatus%2F1874125188855382112%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20appeal%20to%20all%20the%20communities%20in%20the%20state%2C%20whatever%20happened%20has%20happened.%20You%20have%20to%20forgive%20and%20forget%20the%20past%20mistakes%20and%20we%20have%20to%20start%20a%20new%20life%20(towards)%20a%20peaceful%20and%20prosperous%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWhy%20can't%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20go%20to%20Manipur%20and%20say%20the%20same%20thing%20there%3F%20He%20has%20deliberately%20avoided%20visiting%20the%20state%20since%20May%204th%2C%202023%2C%20even%20as%20he%20jets%20around%20the%20country%20and%20the%20world.%20The%20people%20of%20Manipur%20simply%20cannot%20understand%20this%20neglect%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F38lizNtiAy%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F38lizNtiAy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1874041283238650176%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20responded%20with%20a%20jab%2C%20accusing%20the%20Centre%20of%20neglecting%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20go%20to%20Manipur%20and%20say%20the%20same%20thing%20there%3F%20He%20has%20deliberately%20avoided%20visiting%20the%20state%20since%20May%204th%2C%202023%2C%20even%20as%20he%20jets%20around%20the%20country%20and%20the%20world.%20The%20people%20of%20Manipur%20simply%20cannot%20understand%20this%20neglect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20responded%20with%20a%20long%20post%2C%20holding%20Congress%20responsible%20for%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20today.%C2%A0%26quot%3BEveryone%2C%20including%20yourself%2C%20is%20aware%20that%20Manipur%20is%20in%20turmoil%20today%20because%20of%20the%20past%20sins%20committed%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20such%20as%20the%20repeated%20settlement%20of%20Burmese%20refugees%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20SoO%20Agreement%20with%20Myanmar-based%20militants%20in%20the%20state%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20%40PChidambaram_IN%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20Home%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20was%20earlier%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%20after%20disagreements%20with%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20Okram%20Ibobi%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20his%20apology%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsincere%20act%20of%20expressing%20my%20grief%20for%20the%20people%20who%20have%20been%20left%20displaced%20and%20become%20homeless%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20it%20was%20an%20appeal%20to%20forgive%20and%20forget%20what%20had%20happened.%20However%2C%20you%20brought%20politics%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20me%20remind%20you%3A%20The%20Naga-Kuki%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20approximately%201%2C300%20people%20and%20the%20displacement%20of%20thousands%20more.%20The%20violence%20persisted%20for%20several%20years%2C%20with%20periodic%20escalations%20occurring%20between%201992%20and%201997%2C%20though%20the%20most%20intense%20period%20of%20conflict%20was%20in%201992-1993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20clashes%20began%20in%201992%20and%20continued%20at%20varying%20intensities%20for%20around%20five%20years%20(1992-1997).%20This%20period%20marked%20one%20of%20the%20bloodiest%20ethnic%20conflicts%20in%20northeast%20India%2C%20deeply%20affecting%20relations%20between%20the%20Naga%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20in%20Manipur.%20Did%20Shri%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20from%201991%20to%201996%20and%20was%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20during%20this%20time%2C%20come%20to%20Manipur%20to%20extend%20an%20apology%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Kuki-Paite%20clashes%20claimed%20350%20lives%20in%20the%20state.%20During%20most%20of%20the%20Kuki-Paite%20clashes%20(1997-1998)%2C%20Shri%20IK%20Gujral%20was%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20Did%20he%20visit%20Manipur%20and%20say%20sorry%20to%20the%20people%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20putting%20efforts%20to%20solve%20the%20core%20issues%20in%20Manipur%2C%20why%20is%20the%20%40INCIndia%20playing%20politics%20over%20it%20all%20the%20time%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnrest%20in%20Manipur%20has%20claimed%20over%20180%20lives%20since%20May%20last%20year%2C%20when%20violence%20erupted%20over%20the%20Meities%20community's%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20status%20and%20the%20tribal%20Kukis'%20opposition%20to%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735704240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Frsc39d6g_n-biren-singh_625x300_17_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fn-biren-singh-jairam-ramesh-congress-leader-asks-why-pm-didnt-visit-manipur-chief-minister-replies-7374733%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20sharp%20counter%20to%20senior%