5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESteve%20Pemberton%20as%20Titus%20Monroe%20in%20Harlan%20Coben's%20%26quot%3BMissing%20You.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMissing%20You%26quot%3B%20starts%20with%20Kat%20spotting%20Josh%20on%20the%20Melody%20Cupid%20dating%20app.%20But%20it%20emerges%20his%20account%20was%20faked%20as%20part%20of%20an%20extensive%20romance%20scam%20being%20run%20by%20a%20man%20called%20Titus%20Monroe%20(Steve%20Pemberton)%2C%20from%20his%20remote%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20associates%20had%20a%20room%20full%20of%20laptops%2C%20computers%2C%20and%20phones%20that%20they%20used%20to%20lure%20unsuspecting%20single%20people%20into%20fake%20online%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20their%20victims%20were%20invested%2C%20the%20scammers%20invited%20them%20on%20a%20fake%20romantic%20getaway%2C%20kidnapped%20them%2C%20and%20held%20them%20at%20the%20farm%20where%20Titus%20forced%20them%20to%20transfer%20him%20thousands%20of%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20happened%20to%20Rishi%20Maghari%20(Rudi%20Dharmalingam)%2C%20the%20lecturer%2C%20who%20audiences%20meet%20in%20the%20first%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuchanan's%20dating%20profile%20was%20harvested%20from%20a%20Facebook%20account%20made%20by%20his%20secret%20daughter%2C%20Sadie%20(Amelie%20Dokubo)%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20with%20an%20unknown%20woman%20after%20leaving%20Kat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20final%20episode%2C%20the%20scam%20operation%20is%20stopped%20when%20Titus%20realizes%20that%20the%20police%20are%20closing%20in%20and%20he%20burns%20the%20farm%20down.%20He%20tries%20to%20kill%20Dana%20Fells%20(Lisa%20Faulkner)%2C%20one%20of%20his%20scam%20victims%2C%20and%20her%20son%20Brendan%20(Oscar%20Kennedy)%20to%20cover%20his%20tracks.%20But%20Kat%20arrives%20and%20shoots%20Titus%20dead%20before%20he%20can%20kill%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20none%20of%20this%20answers%20the%20key%20mystery%20behind%20Josh's%20disappearance%20or%20Clint's%20death%2C%20it%20just%20ties%20up%20the%20subplot%20regarding%20the%20various%20missing%20people%20that%20Kat%20was%20investigating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2c67569-d2f7-484e-8509-5b2342bf30d9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EClint%20Donovan%20was%20blackmailed%20into%20working%20for%20a%20gangster%20to%20hide%20that%20he%20was%20gay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221709%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Black%20men%20having%20a%20conversation%20in%20the%20street.%20The%20man%20on%20the%20left%20is%20facing%20the%20camera%20and%20has%20a%20shaved%20head%20and%20a%20black%20goatee.%20He's%20wearing%20a%20dark%20blue%20jacket%20and%20a%20light%20blue%20polo%20shirt%20with%20two%20small%20white%20hexagonal%20stripes%20down%20the%20middle.%20The%20other%20man%2C%20who%20has%20his%20back%20to%20the%20camera%2C%20has%20short%20black%20hair%20and%20is%20wearing%20a%20light%20t-shirt.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20silver%20chain%20around%20his%20neck.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6762eef30a6d56a4f9c1ce64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELenny%20Henry%20as%20Clint%20Donovan%20and%20Cyril%20Nri%20as%20Parker%20in%20%26quot%3BMissing%20You.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BMissing%20You%2C%26quot%3B%20Kat%20learns%20that%20her%20father%20was%20a%20corrupt%20officer%20working%20for%20Calligan%20(James%20Nesbitt)%2C%20a%20gangster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20surprise%20because%20Kat%20had%20an%20idealistic%20view%20of%20her%20father%20as%20a%20hardworking%20police%20officer.%20But%20that's%20not%20the%20only%20twist%3A%20Calligan%20points%20her%20toward%20someone%20called%20Parker%20(Cyril%20Nri)%2C%20who%20is%20revealed%20to%20be%20a%20man%20that%20Clint%20was%20having%20an%20affair%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKat%20learns%20that%20her%20father%20was%20secretly%20gay%2C%20and%20Calligan%20was%20using%20that%20to