0here%2C%20and%20we%20just%20felt%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWow%2C%20what%20a%20cool%20place%20to%20go%20during%20Covid.%26quot%3B%20And%20then%20we%20just%20never%20left.%20We%20ended%20up%20having%20our%20son%20here%20and%20built%20a%20house%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20in%20Dorado%2C%20which%20is%20about%2030%20minutes%20to%20the%20west%20of%20San%20Juan%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20really%20big%20community%20of%20people%20who%20have%20relocated%20from%20the%20mainland%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20entrepreneurs.%20It's%20a%20good%20mixture%20of%20us%20and%20locals%20all%20mixed%20together.%20I%20have%20a%20son%20who's%2019%20months%20old%2C%20and%20there%20are%20just%20tons%20of%20other%20kids%20to%20play%20with%20all%20the%20time.%20You%20see%20kids%20ride%20around%20on%20bikes%20by%20themselves.%20It's%20really%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221390%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20Pamplin%20with%20infant%20child%20on%20his%20shoulders%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67748204e5726ab18d0e3930%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221603%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPamplin%2C%20here%20with%20his%20son%2C%20says%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20an%20amazing%20place%20to%20live.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Pamplin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20is%20amazing%20and%20it's%20a%20great%20place%20to%20live%20%E2%80%94%20aside%20from%20the%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20never%20been%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20where%20people%20are%20so%20passionate%20about%20electricity%20that%20they%20protest%20in%20the%20streets%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20moved%20here%2C%20there%20would%20be%20people%20driving%20tons%20of%20cars%2C%20just%20like%20a%20parade%2C%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20megaphones%20and%20noisemakers%20and%20honking%20to%20protest%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-rico-power-outage-hurricane-maria-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epower%20company%20because%20it's%20really%20unreliable%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20it's%20expensive.%20That's%20happened%20many%20times%20since%20we've%20lived%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20mad%20because%20they%20keep%20increasing%20the%20rates%20but%20the%20service%20doesn't%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22adb6ceba-ade5-4fd0-91c2-9cc366a6baca%5C%22%3EBackup%20power%20is%20a%20necessity%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20can%20swing%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20need%20backup%20energy%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20because%20we%20have%20outages%20constantly%2C%20so%20I%20have%20four%20portable%20power%20stations%20and%20two%20backup%20batteries.%20In%20a%20two-week%20period%20recently%2C%20we%20experienced%2014%20outages.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%20it's%20an%20entire%20city%20or%20multiple%20cities.%20Sometimes%20the%20outages%20are%20short%2C%20but%20generally%20they%20last%20five-plus%20hours%2C%20and%20sometimes%20they%20last%2018%20to%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20problem%20for%20so%20many%20people%2C%20and%20for%20restaurants%20and%20local%20businesses%2C%20because%20the%20food%20in%20their%20fridge%20goes%20bad.%20And%20ice%20sells%20out%20super%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20power%20loss.%20Sometimes%20you%20get%20weird%20voltage%20drops%2C%20so%20then%20it%20fries%20all%20your%20electronics.%20You%20might%20not%20even%20be%20able%20to%20get%20it%20fixed%2C%20you%20just%20have%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20one.%20That%20happens%20so%20frequently.%20It's%20happened%20to%20me.%20It's%20happened%20to%20all%20my%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stoplights%20and%20mostly%20unlit%20buildings%20in%20San%20Juan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67747ab59de00e389eb40cfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20stoplights%20were%20out%20and%20most%20buildings%20were%20unlit%20in%20San%20Juan%20on%20Tuesday%20as%20a%20massive%20power%20outage%20swept%20Puerto%20Rico.%3Cp%3ERICARDO%20ARDUENGO%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20the%20gas%20generators%20break%20too.%20These%20generators%20are%20terrible%20environmentally%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20burning%20all%20this%20fuel%2C%20and%20they're%20super%20inefficient.%20It's%20terrible%20for%20the%20air%20quality%20surrounding%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20really%20difficult%20thing%20is%20it's%20really%20hot%20here%20all%20the%20time%20so%20not%20having%20AC%20could%20be%20deadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20enough%20battery%20backup%20for%20the%20ACs%2C%20so%20when%20the%20power%20goes%20off%2C%20I%20usually%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20because%20I%20get%20hot.%20And%20then%20I%20put%20a%20fan%20next%20to%20our%20bed.%20Then%20we%20sneak%20into%20the%20baby's%20room%2C%20trying%20not%20wake%20him%20up%2C%20and%20put%20a%20fan%20next%20to%20his%20bed.%20If%20we%20don't%2C%20he%20can't%20sleep%20at%20all%20without%20a%20fan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20power%20outage%20is%20definitely%20the%20worst%20that%20I've%20seen%20in%20four%20years%20of%20living%20here.%20That's%20because%20it's%20not%20isolated%20to%20one%20city%20or%20one%20area.%20It's%20the%20entire%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20a%20single%20person%20that%20has%20power%20right%20now.%20The%20only%20people%20that%20have%20power%20are%20people%20that%20have%20generators%20or%20they%20have%20powerwalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20never%20seen%20the%20water%20pressure%20drop%20so%20low.%20Right%20now%2C%20my%20water%20pressure%20is%20so%20bad%2C%20not%20just%20because%20my%20pump%20is%20off%2C%20but%20whatever%20pumps%20happen%20at%20the%20water%20company%2C%20those%20pumps%20aren't%20working.%20So%20if%20I%20turn%20on%20my%20faucet%2C%20no%20water%20comes%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20crazy%20to%20live%20in%20a%20place%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20United%20States%20that%20just%2