d%20to%20respect%20each%20other's%20positions%2C%20and%20remain%20humble.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20long%20time%20ago%2C%20somebody%20somewhere%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20taking%20all%20of%20our%20earthly%20possessions%20and%20sharing%20them%20with%20a%20life%20partner.%20Things%20have%20been%20tricky%20ever%20since.%20Especially%20money%20and%20relationships%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20a%20particularly%20difficult%20combination.%20So%20difficult%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20that%2036.1%25%20of%20couples%20cite%20money%20issues%20as%20the%20cause%20of%20their%20divorce.%20This%20staggering%20statistic%20is%20likely%20why%2024%25%20of%20couples%20choose%20not%20to%20share%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20us%2C%20the%20straightforward%20route%20to%20sharing%20life's%20burdens%20with%20our%20partners%20means%20sharing%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20approach%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20chose%20before%20we%20even%20got%20married.%20We%20adopted%20the%20%26quot%3Bwhat's%20yours%20is%20mine%26quot%3B%20attitude%2014%20years%20ago%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20our%20relationship%20shifted%20from%20casual%20to%20serious.%20As%20you%20can%20imagine%2C%20our%20fights%20about%20money%20began%20around%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a85cee3-2829-4abe-bde5-5f0ac5d5687b%5C%22%3EBeing%20a%20spender%2Fsaver%20couple%20isn't%20always%20easy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20might%20think%20that%20choosing%20a%20person%20who%20shares%20the%20same%20goals%20and%20values%20should%20eliminate%20all%20financial%20conflict%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20do%20share%20values%20and%20goals%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20translate%20to%20us%20sharing%20a%20financial%20strategy.%20For%20instance%2C%20we%20both%20value%20comfort%2C%20but%20to%20my%20husband%2C%20comfort%20means%20feeling%20secure%2C%20which%20he%20achieves%20by%20saving%20enough%20money%20to%20handle%20anything%20life%20throws%20at%20him.%20For%20me%2C%20a%20comfortable%20lifestyle%20means%20being%20literally%20physically%20comfortable.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20my%20husband%20is%20a%20saver%2C%20and%20I'm%20a%20spender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20spender%2Fsaver%20dynamic%20is%20likely%20familiar%20to%20anyone%20who%20has%20shared%20finances%20with%20another%20person.%20If%20you're%20the%20saver%2C%20you%20probably%20know%20that%20there%20are%20few%20things%20as%20demoralizing%20as%20checking%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-banks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebank%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20seeing%20a%20smaller%20number%20than%20you%20anticipated%2C%20except%20perhaps%20being%20the%20spender%20who%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20full-grown%20adult%2C%20knows%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20in%20trouble%20for%20treating%20themselves%20to%20an%20%248%20sandwich.%20And%20that's%20the%20thing%20about%20sharing%20finances%3A%20Everyone%20feels%20bad%20all%20the%20time.%20Unless%2C%20of%20course%2C%20you%20find%20a%20way%20to%20make%20it%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20learning%20lessons%20the%20hard%20way%2C%20I%20can%20say%20confidently%20that%20with%20the%20help%20of%20three%20simple%20principles%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20learned%20how%20to%20keep%20the%20peace%20and%20build%20our%20wealth%20as%20a%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217be8d3a-f350-4154-bc4e-abb75d2f5b0b%5C%22%3EThe%203%20rules%20we%20follow%20to%20keep%20the%20peace%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed13a231-3d64-436e-95c4-6e2a6581082d%5C%22%3E1.%20Honesty%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20honesty%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20good%20relationships%20in%20general%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20money%2C%20it%20becomes%20more%20nuanced%20than%20choosing%20not%20to%20message%20an%20ex%20behind%20your%20partner's%20back.%20When%20two%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20share%20money%2C%20the%20struggle%20usually%20stems%20from%20good%2C%20but%20opposing%20best%20intentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20from%20experience%20that%20I've%20often%20justified%20hiding%20purchases%20by%20telling%20myself%20I%20just%20couldn't%20bear%20another%20argument%2C%20while%20savers%20may%20be%20tempted%20to%20hide%20cash%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20protecting%20their%20partner%20from%20themselves.%20But%20when%20we%20strip%20away%20all%20the%20good%20intentions%20and%20justifications%20from%20our%20actions%2C%20we%20are%20left%20with%20lies%2C%20plain%20and%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20marriage%2C%20this%20lying%20and%20sneaking%20around%20not%20only%20eroded%20the%20trust%20we%20shared%2C%20but%20when%20it%20came%20to%20our%20finances%2C%C2%A0%20it%20also%20kept%20us%20from%20fully%20understanding%20our%20financial%20position.%20While%20I%20kept%20my%20husband%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20the%20majority%20of%20my%20purchases%2C%20he%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20began%20over-dramatizing%20our%20bleak%20financial%20outlook%20to%20scare%20me%20out%20of%20spending.%20In%20this%20flurry%20of%20subterfuge%2C%20saving%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-investment-apps-for-beginners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20not%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20honest%20with%20one%20another%2C%20even%20when%20it%20means%20arguing%20and%20relinquishing%20control%2C%20gives%20us%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20how%20much%20money%20we%20have%2C%20how%20much%20money%20we%20spend%2C%20and%20what%20choices%20will%20allow%20us%20to%20reach%20our%20shared%20financial%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f522d1f-a296-489c-9a16-683555b2713c%5C%22%3E2.%20Mutual%20respect%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20a%20nasty%20battle%20over%20whether%20we%20should%20buy%20a%20mattress%20secondhand%2C%20I%20called%20my%20husband%20%26quot%3BScrooge%20McDuck.%26quot%3B%20While%20it%20was%20a%20spiteful%20and%20silly%20dig%2C%20it%20also%20summarizes%20how%20I%20felt%20about%20his%20frugal%20tendencies.%20He%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20felt%20I%20had%20the%20financial%20acumen%20of%20a%207-year-old%20in%20a%20candy%20shop%20with%20%24100%20to%20burn.%20Maybe%20we%20were%20both%20a%20little%20right%2C%20but%20these%20cartoonish%20narratives%20we%20held%20about%20one%20another%20were%20directly%20responsible%20for%20our%20mutual%20dishonesty%20over%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20the%20most%20important%20change%20we%20made%20in%20our%20approach%20to%20sharing%20finances%20was%20recognizing%20that%20our%20spender%2Fsaver%20dynamic%20didn't%20need%20to%20be%20a%20battle%20of%20opposites%2C%20but%20could%20instead%20be%20a%20balance%20of%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20saver%20means%20my%20husband%20is%20always%20wary%20of%20potential%20financial%20hardships.%20This%20vigilance%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20live%20off%20%2410%20an%20hour%20in%20our%20own%20apartment%20rather%20than%20finding%20ourselves%20stuck%20living%20in%20his%20parent's%20basement.%20Someday%2C%20this%20vigilance%20will%20be%20the%20difference%20between%20working%20until%20we%20die%20and%20retiring%20comfortably.%20I'm%20lucky%20to%20have%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20being%20a%20spender%20means%20I%20am%20open%20to%20taking%20financial%20risks%20that%20my%20husband%20would%20have%20been%20too%20scared%20to%20take%20on%20his%20own.%20By%20pushing%20him%20to%20sell%20our%20house%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20market%2C%20I%20made%20us%20%24120%2C000%2C%20and%20I've%20made%20our%20lives%20exponentially%20more%20pleasant%20by%20insisting%20on%20luxuries%20like%20travel%20and%20mattresses%20that%20aren't%20infested%20with%20bedbugs.%20He's%20lucky%20to%20have%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a496c4ea-5bf8-4bb5-a720-0cb41da08ad7%5C%22%3E3.%20Humility%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMutual%20respect%20requires%20more%20than%20recognizing%20what%20the%20other%20person%20has%20to%20offer.%20It%20also%20means%20recognizing%20that%20one%20financial%20style%20isn't%20necessarily%20superior%20to%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20may%20have%20suspected%20based%20on%20my%20%26quot%3BScrooge%20McDuck%26quot%3B%20dig%2C%20my%20instinct%20isn't%20to%20extend%20a%20lot%20of%20respect%20to%20spendthrifts.%20My%20inner%20commentary%20is%20closer%20to%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20another%20tightwad%20who%20thinks%20they're%20going%20to%20become%20a%20billionaire%20by%20sleeping%20on%2080%20thread-count%20sheets%20and%20swapping%20avocado%20toast%20for%20a%20bowl%20of%20gruel.%26quot%3B%20But%20I%20have%20to%20humble%20myself%2C%20quell%20the%20snark%2C%20and%20recognize%20that%20people%20who%20are%20saving%20their%20money%20for%20a%20rainy%20day%20are%20wise%20because%20they're%20right%2C%20rain%20is%20inevitable.%20And%20savers%2C%20as%20my%20husband%20could%20tell%20you%2C%20struggle%20to%20accept%20that%20their%20financial%20caution%20does%20not%20necessarily%20make%20them%20wiser%20than%20their%20%26quot%3Bnow%20is%20now%26quot%3B%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20sense%20of%20superiority%20is%20what%20leads%20us%20to%20dismiss%20what%20our%20partners%20bring%20to%20the%20table%2C%20and%20by%20dismissing%20them%2C%20we%20are%20creating%20an%20environment%20where%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20only%20safe%20play%20is%20to%20hide%2C%20lie%2C%20and%20omit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20to%20agree%20on%20finances%20enough%20to%20build%20wealth%2C%20we%20had%20to%20first%20acknowledge%20that%20our%20individual%20ways%20of%20doing%20things%20weren't%20the%20only%20right%20ones.%20My%20husband%20had%20to%20humble%20himself%20before%20he%20agreed%20to%20sell%20our%20house%2C%20even%20though%20honoring%20his%20hesitance%20felt%20like%20the%20wiser%20choice%20to%20him.%20I%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20had%20to%20swallow%20many%20immediate%20purchases%20I%20felt%20should%20take%20precedence%2C%20to%20do%20things%20my%20husband's%20way%20and%20put%2010%25%20of%20his%20earnings%20toward%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-401k%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E401(k)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20save%20%2460%2C000%20for%20retirement%20in%20five%20years%2C%20and%20I%20no%20longer%20remember%20what%20any%20of%20those%20purchases%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20our%20rules%20are%20simple%20ones%20that%20anyone%20would%20do%20well%20to%20weave%20into%20the%20fabric%20of%20their%20relationship%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20but%20what%20we%20found%20through%20trying%2C%20failing%2C%20and%20trying%20some%20more%20is%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20money%2C%20everything%20becomes%20a%20little%20more%20fraught.%20The%20right%20move%20is%20never%20to%20push%20our%20agenda%20until%20the%20other%20person%20breaks%2C%20but%20to%20do%20our%20best%20to%20be%20our%20best%20for%20each%20other.%20When%20we%20do%20this%2C%20everything%20gets%20easier%2C%20if%20only%20because%20we%20have%20a%20little%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20Exclusive%20Savings%20with%20Raisin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Open%20one%20of%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20best%20savings%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20no-fee%20Raisin%20account%20in%20minutes%20and%20spread%20your%20savings%20across%20an%20exclusive%20network%20of%20over%2030%20FDIC-insured%20banks%20and%20NCUA-insured%20credit%20unions.%20Earn%20top%20savings%20rates%20and%20manage%20it%20all%20with%20a%20single%20secure%20login.%20Read%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fraisin-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERaisin%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20September%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3