20dismissal%20of%20his%20petition%20seeking%20divorce%20on%20grounds%20of%20mental%20cruelty%20and%20desertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Singh-led%20Bench%2C%20in%20its%20judgment%20regarding%20the%20issue%20of%20cruelty%2C%20declined%20to%20accept%20the%20contention%20that%20the%20wife%20had%20been%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfree-willed%20person%E2%80%9D%2C%20who%20would%20go%20out%20on%20her%20own%20to%20the%20market%20and%20other%20places%20and%20did%20not%20observe%20'parda'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20act%20of%20the%20wife%20being%20free-willed%20or%20a%20person%2C%20who%20would%20travel%20on%20her%20own%20or%20meet%20up%20with%20other%20members%20of%20the%20civil%20society%20without%20forming%20any%20illegal%20or%20immoral%20relationship%2C%20may%20not%20be%20described%20as%20an%20act%20of%20cruelty%20committed%2C%20in%20these%20facts%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Binsofar%20as%20such%20acts%20and%20other%20acts%20have%20been%20attributed%20to%20the%20respondent%20(wife)%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20accept%20the%20same%20as%20acts%20of%20cruelty%20committed%2C%20insofar%20as%20both%20parties%20are%20well%20educated.%20The%20appellant%20(husband)%20is%20a%20qualified%20Engineer%2C%20whereas%20the%20respondent%20(wife)%20is%20a%20government%20teacher%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifferences%20of%20perception%20towards%20life%20may%20give%20rise%20to%20different%20behaviours%20by%20individuals.%20Such%20differences%20of%20perception%20and%20behaviour%20may%20be%20described%20as%20cruel%20by%20others%20by%20observing%20the%20behaviour%20of%20another.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20such%20perceptions%20are%20neither%20absolute%20nor%20such%20as%20may%20themselves%20give%20rise%20to%20allegations%20of%20cruelty%20unless%20observed%20and%20proven%20facts%20are%20such%20as%20may%20be%20recognised%20in%20law%20to%20be%20acts%20of%20cruelty%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adde