s%20that%20mere%20possession%20of%20a%20voter%20ID%20card%20does%20not%20guarantee%20the%20right%20to%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20process%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20as%20per%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20electoral%20rolls%20remain%20updated%20and%20inclusive%20for%20all%20eligible%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pre-revision%20period%2C%20house-to-house%20verification%20was%20carried%20out%20from%20August%2020%2C%202024%2C%20to%20October%2018%2C%202024%2C%20by%20Booth%20Level%20Officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20exercise%20aimed%20to%20identify%20unregistered%20eligible%20citizens%2C%20prospective%20voters%20turning%2018%20by%20October%201%2C%202024%2C%20as%20well%20as%20permanently%20shifted%20or%20deceased%20electors%20and%20duplicate%20entries%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20the%20draft%20electoral%20rolls%20were%20published%20on%20October%2029%2C%202024%2C%20inviting%20the%20public%20to%20file%20claims%20and%20objections.%20These%20were%20accepted%20by%20November%2028%2C%202024%2C%20and%20all%20the%20claims%20and%20objections%20received%20were%20already%20disposed%20of%20by%20December%2024%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20electoral%20roll%2C%20reflecting%20these%20updates%2C%20is%20scheduled%20for%20publication%20on%20January%206%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20process%20of%20updation%20of%20rolls%20with%20respect%20to%20addition%2C%20deletion%20and%20modification%20is%20a%20continuous%20activity%20and%20the%20same%20is%20undergoing%20at%20present%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20November%2029%2C%202024%2C%20and%20the%20present%20date%2C%204%2C85%2C624%20applications%20for%20new%20registrations%20(Form%206)%2C%2082%2C450%20applications%20for%20deletions%20(Form%207)%2C%20and%201%2C71%2C385%20applications%20for%20modifications%20(Form%208)%20have%20been%20received%20till%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECitizens%20who%20have%20not%20yet%20registered%20as%20voters%20can%20still%20apply%20for%20enrollment%20using%20Form%206%2C%20which%20requires%20submission%20of%20supporting%20documents%20for%20verification%20by%20the%20respective%20Booth%20Level%20Officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20modifications%20or%20deletions%20in%20the%20electoral%20roll%2C%20Form%208%20and%20Form%207%20can%20be%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20Office%2C%20Delhi%20also%20reminded%20citizens%20that%20having%20multiple%20entries%20in%20the%20electoral%20roll%20or%20multiple%20voter%20ID%20cards%20is%20a%20punishable%20offence%20under%20Sections%2017%20and%2018%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201950.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20FIRs%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20eight%20individuals%20for%20submitting%20false%20documents%20for%20voter%20registration%20in%20the%20Okhla%20Assembly%20constituency%20in%20Delhi.%20Strict%20action%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20taken%20against%20such%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20transparency%20measure%2C%20meetings%20with%20representatives%20of%20political%20parties%20were%20held%20on%20September%204.%20October%209%20and%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20Office%20emphasised%20that%20any%20un-enrolled%20eligible%20citizen%2C%20who%20has%20still%20not%20enrolled%20himself%2Fherself%20in%20the%20electoral%20rolls%2C%20can%20apply%20for%20enrollment%20by%20filing%20Form-6%20along%20with%20supporting%20documents.%20After%20filing%20Form-6%2C%20the%20form%20is%20assigned%20to%20the%20Booth%20Level%20Officer%20(BLO)%20of%20the%20part%20concerned%20for%20field%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20BLO's%20field%20verification%20report%20and%20the%20supporting%20documents%2C%20the%20form%20is%20disposed%20of%20by%20the%20Electoral%20Registration%20Officer%20concerned%20as%20per%20the%20procedure%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20update%20of%20his%2Fher%20name%20in%20the%20electoral%20roll%2C%20an%20EPIC%20PDF%20is%20generated%20and%20sent%20for%20printing.%20After%20receipt%20of%20printed%20EPIC%2C%20the%20same%20is%20delivered%20to%20the%20elector%20through%20post.%20An%20elector%20can%20also%20download%20his%2Fher%20e-EPIC%20from%20the%20ECI's%20portal%20https%3A%2F%2Fvoters.eci.gov.in%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20any%20elector%20has%20permanently%20shifted%20or%20expired%2C%20any%20elector%20of%20that%20particular%20Assembly%20Constituency%20can%20file%20Form%207%20objecting%20to%20such%20entry%20in%20the%20electoral%20roll.%20After%20filing%20Form%207%2C%20notices%20are%20issued%20to%20the%20Objector%20and%20the%20Objectee%20through%20speed%20post%20as%20per%20relevant%20guidelines%20of%20the%20ECI%20except%20for%20registered%20death%20cases.%20If%20the%20elector%20fails%20to%20respond%2C%20the%20name%20is%20deleted%20from%20the%20electoral%20roll%20after%20following%20due%20procedure%20as%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20ECI%20and%20after%20giving%20sufficient%20opportunity%20to%20the%20elector%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735660980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fnphovi6o_up-by-elections_625x300_20_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-elections-2025-a-voter-id-card-does-not-guarantee-right-to-vote-delhi-election-officer-7372369%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%2C%20Delhi%2C%20is%20conducting%20a%20Special%20Summary%20Revision%20of%20electoral%20rolls%20with%20the%20qualifying%20date%20set%20as%20January%201%2C%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-elections-2025-a-voter-id-card-does-not-guarantee-right-