xed%20without%20revealing%20details%20like%20the%20address%20and%20factory%20name%20to%20avoid%20external%20hurdles%20and%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20political%20pressure%20and%20involvement%20of%20goons%20makes%20the%20rescue%20tricky%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shekhar.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20get%20threats%20via%20calls%20and%20messages%3B%20we%20also%20have%20been%20harmed%20and%20threatened%20earlier.%20To%20avoid%20this%2C%20we%20request%20an%20additional%20police%20force%20and%20take%20them%20during%20the%20rescue%20to%20handle%20the%20situation%20effectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20successful%20rescue%2C%20the%20children%20undergo%20a%20thorough%20medical%20examination%20to%20assess%20for%20signs%20of%20abuse%2C%20physical%20and%20mental%2C%20and%20other%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20exposure%20to%20hazardous%20factories%20like%20coating%2C%20steel%2C%20utensils%2C%20embroidery%2C%20and%20the%20like.%20%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20sexual%20abuse%20remains%20a%20significant%20concern%2C%20particularly%20for%20girls%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shekhar%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%20subsequently%20places%20the%20children%20in%20Child%20Care%20Institutes%20(CCIs)%20for%20rehabilitation%20until%20they%20can%20be%20reunited%20with%20their%20families.%20Comprehensive%20counselling%20is%20provided%20for%20both%20the%20children%20and%20their%20parents%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20into%20the%20vicious%20circle%20of%20bonded%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20time%2C%20these%20children%20are%20not%20given%20the%20wages%20for%20the%20tiresome%20work%20done%20but%20are%20underpaid%20and%20forced%20to%20live%20in%20pathetic%20conditions.%20To%20ensure%20the%20children%20receive%20their%20rightful%20compensation%2C%20the%20Labour%20Department%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20settling%20the%20back%20wages%20for%20the%20children%3B%20until%20then%2C%20the%20factory%20remains%20sealed.%20%E2%80%9CHalting%20production%20increases%20the%20financial%20pressure%20on%20the%20factory%20owner%2C%20incentivising%20them%20to%20settle%20the%20outstanding%20payments%20quickly%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Shekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20provide%20ration%20supplies%20enough%20for%20a%20month%20to%20the%20rescued%20children%20as%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20them%20or%20their%20families%20to%20think%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259774%2Fvarghese-child-labour-rescue-ngo-vikasana-chikmagalur-coffee-plantations-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20as%20a%20financial%20burden%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20provide%20whatever%20the%20child%20needs%20%E2%80%94%20clothes%2C%20stationary%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harish%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESharing%20smiles%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20rescue%20mission%20that%20remains%20etched%20in%20Shekhar%E2%80%99s%20memory%20involved%20locating%20a%20nine-year-old%20girl%20working%20as%20a%20domestic%20servant%20in%20North%20Delhi.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20lead%20we%20had%20was%20an%20intermittent%20phone%20number%20provided%20by%20her%20father%2C%20who%20had%20reported%20to%20the%20Odisha%20police%20to%20find%20his%20daughter%2C%20stating%20that%20she%20had%20been%20taken%20away%20for%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20closely%20with%20the%20police%20department%2C%20they%20tracked%20the%20phone%20number%20and%20pinpointed%20the%20general%20location.%20However%2C%20identifying%20the%20individual%20behind%20the%20number%20proved%20challenging%2C%20requiring%20four%20days%20of%20intensive%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDesp