0the%20clouds%2C%20and%20the%20massive%20mountain%20of%20white%20appears%20in%20an%20orange%20silhouette%20as%20an%20alpine%20smell%20takes%20over.%20Many%20have%20called%20it%20%E2%80%98The%20Sleeping%20Buddha%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20lofty%20altitude%20of%203%2C636%20metres%20(11%2C930%20feet)%2C%20Sandakphu%2C%20nestled%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26opi%3D89978449%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374388%2Fnortheast-arunachal-pradesh-sangti-zero-waste-management-community-driven-monpa-sustainability%2F%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjqzNu7tMCKAxWoR2wGHcqDJe4QxfQBKAB6BAgBEAE%26usg%3DAOvVaw0bu9-ij8ownXkMFcux9Okm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEastern%20Himalayas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Darjeeling%20district%2C%20offers%20a%20world%20that%20enchants%2C%20inspires%2C%20excites%2C%20and%20calms%2C%20all%20together%20%E2%80%94%20the%20perfect%20playground%20for%20nature%20enthusiasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20reach%20Sandakphu%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandakphu%20is%20located%20in%20Singalila%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F384072%2Forang-national-park-assam-bengal-tiger-rhinoceros-pygmy-hog-conservation-wildlife-brahmaputra-mini-kaziranga%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Park%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20unique%20sanctuary%20that%20straddles%20the%20Indo-Nepal%20border.%20The%20mighty%20Himalayan%20bear%2C%20the%20elusive%20red%20panda%2C%20and%20the%20rabbit-like%20Pika%20are%20some%20animals%20that%20call%20it%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5